author: Max
description:
Join the hosts for an in-depth look at Watchmen's cultural impact, featuring exclusive insights from Watchmen: Chapter I and Watchmen: Chapter II’s Katee Sackhoff (Silk Spectre) and director Brandon Vietti. Discover how they approached storytelling and animation to create the most faithful adaptation yet with the animated films, Watchmen Chapter I & II.
